    <item>
      <title>Truist 的 Lerner 认为科技股有上涨空间</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-27/truist-s-lerner-sees-upside-in-tech-stocks-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Truist Advisory 首席市场策略师 Keith Lerner 表示，第四季度趋势向好，但随着总统大选临近，可能会出现“直觉判断”。他还认为科技股有上涨空间。他在“彭博未平仓合约”上发表了讲话。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-27/truist-s-lerner-sees-upside-in-tech-stocks-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 16:48:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大众汽车因汽车需求减弱再次下调利润预测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/volkswagen-lowers-forecast-again-on-waning-car-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于乘用车需求疲软，大众汽车集团今年第二次下调年度业绩预期，这对陷入困境的德国汽车行业而言是最新打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/volkswagen-lowers-forecast-again-on-waning-car-sales</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 16:38:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>赞比亚同意与中国贷款机构达成 15 亿美元债务重组协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/zambia-agrees-1-5-billion-debt-revamp-with-chinese-lenders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[赞比亚财政部长西图姆贝科·穆索科特瓦内 (Situmbeko Musokotwane) 表示，赞比亚已与两家中国国有银行达成 15 亿美元债务重组协议，这是朝着完成长达数年的债务重组进程迈出的重要一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/zambia-agrees-1-5-billion-debt-revamp-with-chinese-lenders</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 16:06:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>科技股拖累股市；国债延续涨势：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于最新的通胀数据并未改变人们对美联储政策走向的预期，美国国债价格继续上涨，而美国股市则出现波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 22:40:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大高收益债券市场突然成为多年来最热门的市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/canada-s-junk-bond-market-is-suddenly-the-hottest-in-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经常被忽视的加拿大高收益债券市场正在迎来机遇，因为各大公司纷纷涌入出售债券，而投资者则希望在央行货币政策放松之前锁定息票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/canada-s-junk-bond-market-is-suddenly-the-hottest-in-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 16:58:29 GMT</pubDate>
